<entry valign="top" align="left"><list id="fs-idm190351424" list-type="bulleted" bullet-style="bullet">
<item>An informal agreement between customer and company</item>
<item>Receivable in less than one year or within a company’s operating cycle</item>
<item>Does not include interest</item>
