<para id="fs-idm211364032"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67886"/>A company collects an honored note with a maturity date of 24 months from establishment, a 10% interest rate, and an initial loan amount of $30,000. Which accounts are used to record collection of the honored note at maturity date?</para>
