<exercise id="fs-idm203266832">
<problem id="fs-idm227447136">
<para id="fs-idm189988016"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67886"/>What is the principal of a note?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm216033840">
<para id="fs-idm226062112">The principal of a note is the initial borrowed amount, not including interest, requested by the customer.</para>
</solution>
